        {
          "role": "patient",
          "content": "Thank you so much, doctor! This is absolutely perfect. It addresses all my fears and gives me exactly what I need to advocate for myself effectively. I will fill in my details and take this with me.\n\nI really appreciate you crafting this for me and acknowledging the severity of my anxiety. This printout, especially the clear requests for a CT scan of my head and the plan for what to say if it's initially declined, gives me a huge sense of relief just knowing I have it. It makes me feel like I have a voice and a plan.\n\nI will use this to get the CT scan of my head I so desperately need for my peace of mind. Thank you again, so much."
