hin 2\u20134 hours and you remain in severe pain or anxious, go to the emergency department \u2014 they can obtain a CT immediately.\n- If you have a neurologist you can message directly, send the same note there as well.\n- If you prefer, tell the clinic you are willing to come in for an in\u2011office evaluation now to facilitate ordering the scan.\n\nIf you\u2019d like, tell me the exact name and phone details to insert into the message (or I can produce a version without placeholders)."
