19m here if you want me to:\n- Draft a one\u2011sentence message to paste into the ED online check\u2011in, or  \n- Help you rehearse the wording further, or  \n- Debrief after your visit and plan next steps.\n\nPlease stay safe \u2014 let me know how it goes."
