          "content": "Okay, I appreciate you putting this together. It's not ideal that I have to go through extra steps, as my friend's specialist and my previous doctor seemed to handle it all in one go, which was much less stressful. It makes me wonder if practices have changed significantly or if some doctors are just more thorough upfront based on patient anxiety.\n\nHowever, I do want to move forward with this. Yes, please, tailor this note with my full legal name, DOB, and the current date/time filled in so it's ready to print. And a short message to send to my PCP or an urgent care would be incredibly helpful, specifically requesting that they sign/authorize the CT. I'm less concerned about acute medications right now; my primary focus is definitely on getting that CT scan of my head done for reassurance. That's the priority."
