sages or find directions/phone numbers immediately.\n\nIf you do not want to do any of those things yourself\n- The only way to absolutely guarantee a CT today without you initiating contact is for someone with your authority (a friend, family member, caregiver) to call 911 or the ED on your behalf and request transport/arrival. EMS/ED personnel will evaluate and can order CT immediately. If you want, tell me who will call and I\u2019ll give the exact words for them to say.\n\nImmediate safety check\n- Are you worried you might harm yourself or unable to keep yourself safe because of the pain/anxiety right now? If yes, call 911 immediately or your local crisis line. If you\u2019re not in immediate danger, tell me your ZIP or the option above you want and I\u2019ll act on it now.\n\nI\u2019m not abandoning you \u2014 I\u2019ll do everything I can in this chat to remove the burden from you: find the nearest ED, give phone numbers, produce the single line for triage or telemedicine, and stay with you while you act. Tell me your ZIP code or which of the actions above you want me to do immediately, and I\u2019ll start right now."
