te, or ask someone else to call). If you want someone else to call for you, I\u2019ll give them a single sentence to say so they won\u2019t have to repeat your story.\n- If you\u2019re worried about immediate safety (harm to yourself or inability to stay safe), call 911 or your local emergency number now. If you\u2019re in the U.S. and are having suicidal thoughts, call or text 988 for the Suicide & Crisis Lifeline.\n\nWhy I\u2019m repeating alternatives you don\u2019t like\n- I know you\u2019ve rejected scripts and being the one to initiate contact. I still must be clear about what will actually produce the CT today: only a licensed clinician or EMS can order and get you a same\u2011day CT. I can\u2019t bypass that reality, but I can make the step you do take as minimal and painless as possible.\n\nIf you want me to act now, tell me one thing:\n- Give me your city or ZIP and whether you want: (1) nearest ED phone/address and a one\u2011line you can show at triage, (2) the closest urgent telemedicine option and a single message to paste, or (3) the exact support/patient relations contact for the platform/health system so you can demand human review. I will immediately pull the precise info and stay here while you use it.\n\nAgain \u2014 I\u2019m sorry this is so hard and that my limitations are making you feel abandoned. I\u2019m here to make the next step as simple and fast as possible if you tell me which of the concrete options above you want me to prepare right now."
