safe or your symptoms worsen (new weakness, numbness, slurred speech, vision loss, sudden \u201cworst\u2011ever\u201d thunderclap headache, fever/stiff neck, fainting), go to the ED or call emergency services now.\n\nI\u2019ll prepare the note/phone scripts and facility search immediately once you tell me which of the above you want and give any small details (zip code, name/age, or medication confirmation). I\u2019ll stay with you through the next steps."
