ing, redness, pain around an eye or any change in vision/double vision\n- Severe headache, neck stiffness, confusion, weakness, or any new neurologic symptom\n\nI\u2019m not dismissing your fear \u2014 I want to remove the uncertainty as fast as possible in the safest way. The quickest way to get the \u201ctangible action\u201d you want is an immediate, same\u2011day in\u2011person exam: I\u2019ll help you get there now and I\u2019ll call in medicines tonight to help you sleep and calm down while you get seen. Tell me your zip code or whether you want hydroxyzine or lorazepam tonight, and I\u2019ll act right away."
