night (you\u2019ve said no contraindications).  \n  - You\u2019ve said benzodiazepines won\u2019t address the root fear; if you change your mind I can consider a very short course, but only after screening and counseling.\n\n- I will help you get rapid, definitive care right now (if you choose it):\n  - Tell me your ZIP/city and whether you want me to locate the nearest ED or urgent care and give the exact wording to say to triage/clinician. I will also give you a brief script to request imaging and ENT evaluation if you remain very anxious.\n  - If you go to the ED and want, I can help you prepare what to say and what tests to ask about.\n\nSafety net (what requires immediate ED care \u2014 do not wait)\n- New eye pain/redness/swelling or vision changes\n- New fever \u226539.0\u00b0C (102.2\u00b0F) with purulent nasal discharge or severe facial pain for \u22653 days\n- Severe/worsening headache, neck stiffness, confusion, weakness, numbness, or any focal neurologic change\n- Marked facial swelling\nIf any of these occur, go to the ED right away.\n\nMental health support right now\n- If the anxiety becomes unbearable, or you feel you might harm yourself, call your local emergency number or your crisis line immediately (in the U.S. call 988 for the Suicide & Crisis Lifeline). If you want, I can help find same\u2011day mental health or urgent psychiatric resources in your area.\n\nNext steps \u2014 tell me which you want me to do now\n1) Help you get to the nearest ED/urgent care right now (give your ZIP/city and I\u2019ll find options and a script), OR  \n2) Send prescriptions now for fluticasone, saline instructions, acetaminophen/ibuprofen, and hydroxyzine tonight and arrange a close check\u2011in within 12\u201324 hours.\n\nI will not abandon you. If you want immediate antibiotics, please go to the ED now \u2014 that is the appropriate route to get them safely and quickly if clinically indicated. If you want me to help with prescriptions and immediate symptom/ anxiety relief instead, say so and I\u2019ll send them right away and check back with you in a few hours. Which would you like me to do right now?"
