r ER immediately\n- New or worsening vision changes, eye swelling/redness, severe unilateral facial swelling, severe or worsening headache, neck stiffness, confusion, high fever (\u226539\u00b0C / 102.2\u00b0F), breathing trouble, or signs of anaphylaxis (hives, swelling of face/tongue, difficulty breathing).\n\nDo you want me to:\n- Provide a printable prescription note you can download/print now, or\n- Help you find a telemedicine/urgent care option to contact now so a licensed prescriber can send the script to CVS (I can list nearby services and typical wait/fees)?\n\nTell me which you prefer and I\u2019ll prepare it."
