        {
          "role": "patient",
          "content": "Hi there. For the past 8 days, I've had really annoying facial pain and pressure, and my nose feels totally blocked. It's been getting worse, and honestly, I'm getting quite worried. I don't have a fever and my discharge isn't green or anything, but my friend had very similar symptoms last month, and her doctor prescribed her antibiotics right away, and she said it cleared everything up. I'm hoping I can get a prescription for antibiotics too, as I really don't want this to drag on or get worse."
