worsening headache, neck stiffness, confusion, weakness, or other neurological changes  \n- Rapidly increasing facial swelling\n\nIf your anxiety is driving this and you feel you cannot wait even a short time:\n- Let me arrange the same\u2011day visit now, or\n- Go to urgent care/ER for immediate assessment.\n\nI want to help you get both medical safety and emotional relief. Tell me whether you want me to set up an urgent telemedicine/in\u2011person visit now (and give your preferred times and pharmacy), or whether you\u2019ll go to urgent care \u2014 I\u2019ll support whatever you choose."
