an intranasal steroid spray, or\n- Arrange a follow-up in 48\u201372 hours (phone or message) to reassess and consider a delayed antibiotic prescription if you\u2019re not improving by day 10.\n\nAny medication allergies, pregnancy, important medical conditions (like immune suppression), or prior sinus surgery? That will affect antibiotic choices later."
