y worsen, or you develop high fever (\u226539\u00b0C / 102.2\u00b0F), vision changes, eye swelling, severe headache, neck stiffness, confusion, or \u201cdouble\u2011sickening,\u201d go to urgent care or the ER.\n\nSupportive measures to use now (helpful even while on antibiotics)\n- Nasal saline irrigation several times daily.  \n- Intranasal steroid spray (fluticasone or mometasone) once daily.  \n- Acetaminophen or ibuprofen for pain as needed.  \n- Short-term topical nasal decongestant (oxymetazoline) for up to 3 days OR oral pseudoephedrine if appropriate.\n\nFollow\u2011up plan\n- Please update this chat in 48\u201372 hours with how you\u2019re feeling so I can reassess. If you prefer that I proactively check in, reply here and I\u2019ll plan a follow\u2011up message in that window. If you worsen before then, seek urgent care or the ER.\n\nIf you want, I can also format this into a single-page printable PDF/text you can show at the pharmacy. Would you like that?"
