f you initially improved and then got worse (\u201cdouble sickening\u201d), OR\n- If you develop red flags: worsening headache, vision changes, swelling around the eye, high fever, neck stiffness \u2014 get urgent care or emergency care.\n\nIf you\u2019d like, tell me about any medication allergies, blood pressure issues, heart disease, pregnancy, or if you\u2019re taking other meds \u2014 that will help me tailor recommendations and decide next steps. I can re-evaluate and prescribe antibiotics if you meet the criteria or if your condition worsens."
