today so I or another clinician can assess and prescribe if appropriate. I\u2019m happy to arrange that for you now.\n\nBefore we proceed I need to know:\n- Any drug allergies (especially penicillin/cephalosporins)?  \n- Are you pregnant or breastfeeding?  \n- Do you have high blood pressure, heart disease, liver disease, or other chronic conditions?  \n- What other medications do you take?\n\nIf you\u2019re developing any of these urgent signs, go to the ER now: vision changes, eye swelling/redness, severe/worsening headache, neck stiffness, high fever, confusion, or difficulty breathing.\n\nI want you to get relief safely \u2014 tell me whether you want me to arrange an urgent in\u2011person visit now or whether you\u2019ll accept the symptomatic measures and close follow\u2011up. I\u2019ll act immediately on whichever you choose."
