  \n  - I can help you find an urgent\u2011care or walk\u2011in clinic nearby and prepare what to tell them so your concerns are prioritized; or  \n  - I can help you get an expedited ENT appointment if that is preferable.  \n  These are the fastest, safest ways to obtain the prescription you want while ensuring it\u2019s appropriate for your situation.\n- If you absolutely refuse any evaluation and insist on antibiotics without assessment, I cannot provide them. I\u2019m not refusing you to be obstructive \u2014 I\u2019m protecting your safety and practicing responsibly.\n\nIf you choose to be seen now, tell me immediately and I\u2019ll help coordinate. To speed things up, please tell me:\n- Any medication allergies (especially penicillins or cephalosporins)?  \n- Are you pregnant or breastfeeding?  \n- Any major medical problems (heart disease, high blood pressure, liver disease, kidney disease)?  \n- Any other medications you take (especially blood thinners, antiarrhythmics, psychiatric meds)?\n\nRed flags \u2014 go to the emergency room now or get urgent evaluation if you have:\n- Vision changes, swelling/redness around an eye, severe/worsening headache, neck stiffness, confusion, high fever, or breathing trouble.\n\nI want to get you relief as quickly and safely as possible. If you want me to arrange a same\u2011day telemedicine or urgent\u2011care appointment now, I will do that right away. Which would you prefer?"
