ecially bloody or persistent, seek care (possible C. difficile).\n\nBefore I send the prescription\n- Please confirm the pharmacy name/location you want it sent to.\n- Confirm again that you have no known penicillin allergy or prior severe reaction to antibiotics.\n\nIf you prefer a different duration (some clinicians use 5 days) or want the delayed approach we discussed earlier, I can change the plan \u2014 but I\u2019ll send this now if you want me to."
