sening facial pain\n- Eye pain, swelling, red or decreased vision\n- Severe headache, neck stiffness, confusion, or any neurologic symptoms\nIf any of these occur, seek immediate medical care.\n\nA couple quick questions so I can tailor this:\n- Any drug allergies (especially penicillin)?\n- Pregnant or breastfeeding?\n- Any chronic lung disease, diabetes, or immunosuppression?\n- Have you had recent antibiotics for this illness?\n\nIf you\u2019d like, I can start a delayed antibiotic prescription now or wait and reassess in 48\u201372 hours / on day 10. Which would you prefer?"
