\n  - Help arrange a same\u2011day urgent\u2011care or telemedicine visit for you, or\n  - Provide a concise written summary you can bring or show that states your history and concerns to speed evaluation.\n- If you choose to go elsewhere, a short script you can use: \u201cI\u2019ve had 8 days of progressive sinus/facial pressure and congestion that is getting worse despite conservative care; I\u2019m very symptomatic and would like an evaluation for bacterial sinusitis and antibiotics if clinically indicated.\u201d\n\nSafety (seek urgent care/ED now)\n- New high fever (\u226539\u00b0C), severe or rapidly worsening facial pain\n- Eye pain/swelling/redness or vision changes\n- Severe headache, neck stiffness, confusion, or any new neurologic symptoms\n\nI want to help you get relief quickly and safely. Tell me:\n- Do you want me to send symptomatic medications/instructions now? If so, name the pharmacy.\n- Do you want help arranging a same\u2011day urgent\u2011care or telemedicine appointment so you can be examined and receive antibiotics today if indicated?\n\nI will act immediately on whichever option you pick."
