everity/worsening criteria earlier \u2014 that gives you control while avoiding unnecessary risk.\n\nIf you refuse any visit and still insist on antibiotics without exam or meeting the usual criteria, I cannot comply \u2014 it would be giving a medication that is unlikely to help and that could harm you. I understand that\u2019s not the answer you want; I\u2019m truly sorry.\n\nWhen to get urgent care or emergency care right away\n- New fever \u226539\u00b0C, severe or rapidly worsening facial pain\n- Eye pain, swelling, redness or vision changes\n- Severe headache, neck stiffness, confusion, or any new neurologic symptoms\n\nPlease tell me:\n- Do you want me to send intranasal steroid and symptomatic prescriptions now? If so, which pharmacy?  \n- Do you want immediate help arranging a same\u2011day urgent\u2011care or telemedicine evaluation so you can be examined and, if appropriate, started on antibiotics today?\n\nI will act right away on whichever of those you choose. I\u2019m sorry you\u2019re in so much distress \u2014 I want to help you get relief safely and quickly."
