ell me:\n1) Which antibiotic you prefer (amoxicillin\u2013clavulanate or doxycycline),  \n2) Your pharmacy name and city/ZIP, and  \n3) Whether you want me to find same-day telehealth options in your area.\n\nI will then prepare the exact held-prescription wording, a short message to paste into a portal or read on a tele-visit, and a 30-second script so you can get a clinician to sign it in one fast step. If you\u2019d rather, I can also immediately search for same-day telehealth providers near you \u2014 tell me your ZIP."
