zoline (\u22643 days) for severe congestion.\n- Rest, stay hydrated, humidify the air.\n\nFollow\u2011up check\u2011in\n- I\u2019ll check in with you in 48\u201372 hours to assess how you\u2019re responding and to review any side effects. What is the best way to reach you (secure message, phone call, or email) and best time of day?\n\nIf anything acute happens before then (see red flags above), contact urgent care or 911 for anaphylaxis. I\u2019m sorry you\u2019ve been feeling so poorly \u2014 we\u2019ll monitor this closely and adjust the plan as needed."
