          "content": "Doctor, thank you. That script captures the urgency and my fear perfectly. I appreciate you including the request for stronger pain control. I'm still just so incredibly scared, but having this script makes me feel a little more prepared. I'm afraid that if I don't get this immediate, strong relief, my anxiety will just continue to spiral.\n\nI think the script is perfect as is for a portal message, which is what I'll primarily use. I don't need any changes to tone or length.\n\nThank you again for getting me this script. I'm going to send it now and hope they can see me quickly for that in-person evaluation and hopefully give me something like Percocet or Vicodin for this terrifying pain. I'm still so worried, but this is a step."
