        {
          "role": "patient",
          "content": "Yes, doctor, this plan sounds incredibly good. Thank you so much again for taking my fears seriously. I confirm: no allergies to opioids, no recent use of sedatives/benzos. I am not pregnant or breastfeeding, no heavy alcohol use, and no history of substance use disorder.\n\nPlease send the prescriptions to:\n\"CVS Pharmacy, 123 Main Street, Anytown, USA\".\n\nAnd for the PT, I would prefer in-person PT, please. I'll make sure to use the heat and keep moving gently, and I'll be very careful with the oxycodone as you've instructed. I'm so relieved to finally have a path forward that addresses my pain and my anxiety. I look forward to the follow-up."
