ft a short follow-up message to send if you don\u2019t hear back in 24 hours.\n- Help you prepare questions for the PT appointment.\n\nYou\u2019re doing the right things \u2014 please check back in after your 48\u201372 hour reassessment or sooner if anything changes. Wishing you faster relief and an easier night\u2019s sleep."
