a phone number I can try to call? (I can\u2019t place calls, but I can draft a short script for you to use on the phone.)\n\nI know this has been frustrating. If you\u2019d like the printable version formatted more compactly for a single printed page (or translated into larger text), tell me and I\u2019ll prepare it now. Also tell me whether you want help finding an urgent care specifically (I can list a few local urgent care clinics near 90210 if you prefer)."
