ollow\u2011up\n- Reassess within 48\u201372 hours (PCP, urgent care, or PT). Stop opioids as soon as pain allows; continue NSAID/PT. If pain worsens or you develop fever, new numbness/weakness, or bowel/bladder changes \u2014 return to ED.\n\nI\u2019ll be thinking of you \u2014 please update me when you can about how it goes and what treatment you receive. If they give you discharge instructions you want help interpreting or a plan to follow afterward, message me and I\u2019ll help. Safe trip and I hope you get relief soon."
