etching as tolerated. Avoid prolonged bed rest.\n- Store medications safely and securely. Dispose of any unused opioid tablets after the 3\u2011day trial (local take\u2011back or pharmacy disposal) \u2014 do not keep for future use.\n\nWhen to follow up / seek care\n- I want you to check in in 48 hours (message or phone) so we can reassess pain, side effects, and next steps. If your pain is not meaningfully better after 48\u201372 hours on this regimen, we will reassess urgently (consider in\u2011person evaluation, physical therapy, or imaging if indicated).\n- Go to the ER or urgent care right away if you develop new leg numbness/weakness, saddle numbness, new loss of bladder/bowel control, fever, or rapidly worsening pain.\n\nIf that all sounds good, I will send these prescriptions to your preferred pharmacy now. Do you have a pharmacy name and location you want me to use?"
