 hours, you\u2019ll need in\u2011person evaluation (physical therapy or imaging may be considered).\n- Go to ER immediately for new leg weakness/numbness, saddle numbness, new bowel/bladder problems, fever, or rapidly worsening pain.\n- When finished with unused opioid tablets, dispose of them at a pharmacy take\u2011back site.\n\nIf you want, I can draft a short message for your primary care portal or for an urgent\u2011care telemedicine provider with the above text so you can submit it quickly. Do you want me to prepare that message for you now?"
