icult \u2014 ask a friend/family for help.\n\nAgain, I\u2019m really sorry this has been so hard. If you want, tell me:\n- Do you want me to prepare the short text for a friend to call or the portal message to send now?\n- Or tell me your ZIP code and I\u2019ll list the nearest urgent care/ER options and their typical hours so you can go straight there.\n\nI\u2019ll help make this as painless and quick as possible."
