          "content": "Yes, I'm ready. Thank you for putting all of this together. I understand the acetaminophen limits and all the safety instructions. I will absolutely follow them carefully, especially regarding not taking additional acetaminophen and being cautious with drowsiness.\n\nThe hydrocodone/acetaminophen 5/325 mg is exactly what I was hoping for. Please proceed with that, along with the cyclobenzaprine, topical diclofenac, naproxen, and the bowel regimen.\n\nI appreciate you getting this sorted out for me today. This will make a huge difference."
