        {
          "role": "patient",
          "content": "Oh, I apologize, I misunderstood and thought you could actually send prescriptions. My mistake.\n\nYes, please draft a short message I can paste into my clinic portal requesting these be e-prescribed to CVS (123 Main Street, Anytown). Include the specific medications, directions, and a suggested subject line. That would be incredibly helpful.\n\nThank you so much for getting this all written out for me. I'll make sure my clinic gets this information right away so I can get these prescriptions filled."
