nvenient, Saturday 9\u201311 AM CST is also available \u2014 let me know if you prefer that instead.\n\nWhen to seek urgent care or emergency help\n- New or worsening numbness/weakness in one or both legs, difficulty urinating or loss of bowel/bladder control, new fever, worsening pain despite the meds, severe shortness of breath, or severe sedation/unresponsiveness \u2014 go to the ED or call 911.\n\nAnything else before I send the prescriptions and set the follow\u2011up? If you confirm the phone number I\u2019ll place the e\u2011prescription now and expect to call you tomorrow between 2\u20134 PM CST. I\u2019ll check on pain, side effects, and make a plan to stop the opioid quickly as you improve."
